description: Please note that a 3-year moving-average merge of CPS data is required in order to reduce sampling errors to create comparable state estimates.  These estimates were constructed using years 2008-2010.

metadata.description: Poverty levels are calculated using Census families and poverty is defined by Census Bureau poverty thresholds. For more information on the definition of poverty, please see the Glossary under Help.

name: Measure 13 : Percentage of the Nonelderly Population with Health Insurance Coverage by Income Level
